Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case takes place\Nin a high-rise building!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These elevators bear a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when hidden behind double doors,\Nthere's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Elevator Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:02.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Exit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:12.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fitting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's a holiday!\NWhy's there so much traffic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it wouldn't\Nhave been faster by train?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a model for Ashiya-san's clothing--\Nit's like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure this is Ashiya Eiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...One of the top fashion\Ndesigners in Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:03:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Ashiya Eiko the one whose\Nfashion show was cancelled recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rival company announced\Na winter clothing line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,very similar to the latest line\Nthat she was going to have at her show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she had no choice but to cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know a lot about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're actually\Nan Ashiya Eiko fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! A detective\Nmust always expand his horizons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep on top of what's going on\Nin the world around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one big building...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to be\Na model yourself, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that! You're really\Nstarting to get on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! My name's Mori Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, we've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The company president will be back soon.\NPlease wait over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, today's a holiday,\Nso there's no one else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry to keep you waiting, Ran-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are big purses the latest style now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her life revolves around all\Nthe up-and-coming fashions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll catch on soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my father and Conan Edogawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They absolutely\Ninsisted on coming with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Kogoro, at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving\Nmy daughter this opportunity--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Kogoro? The famous detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've heard of me!\NWhat an honor this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are a token of my admiration.\NPlease accept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashiya-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my secretary,\NTaniguchi Mika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mori Ran-san\Nand her father, Kogoro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to call you here on a Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I'll just quit\Nas soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I am being forced\Nto work on weekends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go put these flowers in\Nmy office and bring back the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a seat there with\Nyour father and Conan-kun while you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika-san. Go to the 8th floor\Nfitting room and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:06:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but is\Nthat secretary quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's apparently already\Nturned in her letter of resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem on such bad terms,\Nbut she still pushed the button for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct elevator to the 15th floor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct elevator to the 8th floor\N(Stops at each floor coming down)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's wait over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first I need to use the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you both remember\Nto wash your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called Mika-san's cell phone\Nfrom my office, but she won't answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come look with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she so worked up about\Nsomeone not answering their phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elevator Taniguchi-san\Nused is stuck on the 8th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could something have happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's take this elevator up\Nand see for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Eiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secretary, Taniguchi Mika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! There are footprints on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Footprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem they were made\Nby dust from the emergency stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A robber must've broke inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They snuck in, found Mika-san,\Nand then stabbed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like she knew this\Nwould happen to Taniguchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eda-san! Could you stop the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These footprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stabbed through the heart.\NDied almost instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These footprints are\N26 centimeters in length.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,26 centimeters, eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a blood stain on her shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this crease doing\Non the shoulder of her jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone working in the\Noverly conscious fashion industry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wear something with\Na crease like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the strangest thing is that\NTaniguchi-san is lying on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,facing away from the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she was stabbed\Nas she got off the elevator,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she would have collapsed inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, the killer must've\Npurposely pulled her into the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would they need to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Taniguchi-san were riding\Nin different elevators, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That elevator was the one I took.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 15th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This goes non-stop to the 15th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this center elevator is\Nthe one Taniguchi Mika-san took?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one's non-stop to the 8th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then it can go floor-by-floor,\Nall the way to the 15th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the one we took just\Nnow stops at the 8th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then comes back down\Nin single-floor increments...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two elevators can\Ngo to the 15th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much time passed from when\NAshiya-san first got into the elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until she returned here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a little more\Nthan one minute, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little under two minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency stairwell exit\Non the 1st floor was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you last do your rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 2 hours before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain the door was locked then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone enter or leave\Nthe building afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody except the company president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I needed to check something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived about an hour ago\Nand was in my office for half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I left to get some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left through the main entrance,\Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! I think Eiko-san is right--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was the work of a burglar\Nbreaking into the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer unlocked the 1st floor\Nemergency exit from the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took the stairs to the 8th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, just as he passed\Nby the elevators...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he ran into Taniguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He murdered her,\Nthen escaped back down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Search the\Nnearby vicinity immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'll need to take\Nyour fingerprints, Ashiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that I'm the murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to distinguish between\Nthe killer's fingerprints and yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's no way you could\Npossibly have been the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eiko-san and Taniguchi-san got\Nin different elevators at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taniguchi-san arrived at the 8th floor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was murdered immediately\Nafter the doors opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Eiko-san\Nwas on the 15th floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there was no elevator\Nto take her to the 8th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how could she have\Nkilled Taniguchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't clear her\Nof all suspicion--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a kid--\Ndon't tell a pro how to do his job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no excuse for hitting him, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he just won't learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lost cause!\NCan't depend on him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm right, the key to solving\Nthis case should be on the 15th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! The company president's floor\Nsure is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What fancy carpeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower petal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pollen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tape marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,President's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same pollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was there a flower petal\Nand pollen here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't have passed by here\Nif she went straight to her office...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taniguchi-san was killed inside\Nthis elevator on the 8th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashiya Eiko-san was all\Nby herself for just over a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking the stairs to the 8th floor,\Nkilling her, and then coming back up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would take at least 4 or 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that the question here\Nis where exactly she was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way her body\Nwas lying on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood stain and the unnaturally\Ncrumpled part of her jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower petal lying on the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the tape marks around\Nthe call button for the elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Taniguchi-san was in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an alibi trick\Ninvolving elevators!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taniguchi-san's murderer\Nwas indeed Ashiya Eiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No fingerprints at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. There were none on the knife\Nnor on the 1st floor emergency exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Inspector.\NWould it be all right if I went home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. That should\Nbe enough for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! If she goes,\Nshe'll dispose of the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other choice!\NI'll have to use the old man again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but can we do this another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll just be going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to see you to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Which is what I would like to say,\Nbut we cannot allow you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason being...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you're the one\Nwho murdered Taniguchi Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Mori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who just explained\Nwhy she couldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, allow me to explain those\Nfootprints in the 8th floor hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat, if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a ruse she concocted\Nto make Taniguchi Mika-san's murder
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look like the result of\Na burglar breaking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to remember what\Nthose footprints looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, someone would run away\Nafter committing a murder, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This would cause the footprints\Nto be far apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, these footprints\Nwere made by someone walking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on both their way into\Nand out of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Now that you mention it,\Nyou're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You entered the building\Nan hour before the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,made the fake footprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then unlocked the 1st floor\Nemergency exit from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, you hid the sneakers\Nthat don't fit you inside your large purse
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then left the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back 30 minutes later,\Nafter you had disposed of the sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then as we looked on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you headed for the elevator hall\Nwith Taniguchi Mika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who\Npressed the call button.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason being that you needed her\Nto use the center elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of the one\Nthat was nearest to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the elevator, you started\Ndialing her number on your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After getting off on the 15th floor,\Nyou pressed the dial button.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for cell phones to connect\Nwhile inside elevators, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told Taniguchi-san to come\Nto the 15th floor right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, you taped a coin to\Nthe call button on the 15th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did this to make sure the\Nelevator doors wouldn't close
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you were killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.11,0:17:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-kun! The victim was\Nfound dead on the 8th floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we come to the\Nmain point of the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you find the direction\Nshe was lying strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she had been stabbed by someone\Nas she was getting off the elevator,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she would have fallen back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was lying outside of the elevator,\Nfacing away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eiko-san stabbed Taniguchi-san\Non the 15th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got behind her, and then turned her\Nin the direction of the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she pressed the button\Nfor the 8th floor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and removed the tape\Nfrom the call button.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She then propped Taniguchi-san up\Nin a sitting position
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent her down to the 8th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she\Nwould do such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two keys to unraveling\Nthe mystery behind this alibi trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first was the crease on the\Nshoulder of Taniguchi-san's jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was created when the jacket was\Ncaught between the elevator doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second key was in the flower petal\Nand pollen left on the carpet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Eiko-san put\Nthe bouquet on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it wouldn't get in the way\Nof killing Taniguchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an interesting story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's nothing but a theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if Taniguchi-san rode\Nthe 8th floor elevator a second time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her fingerprint should have been\Non the 8th floor call button.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any fingerprints on the call button?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No fingerprints at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mori-san.\NTaniguchi-san didn't go to the 15th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your theory has been disproved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Because you removed\Nher fingerprint yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly stupendous execution, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to close the elevator doors,\Nyou pressed the call button
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then removed her fingerprint\Nby wiping it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Does that mean\Nthere's no proof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's proof all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside Eiko-san's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of proof?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bloody gloves she used\Nwhen committing the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time-wise, she shouldn't have\Nbeen able to dispose of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she couldn't dare hide\Nthem inside the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were more than confident\Nabout your elevator alibi trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the only possibility\Nis that the bloodied gloves
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are in your possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who stole your design\Nand sold it to that rival company...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was Taniguchi Mika-san, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. The evidence is here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I did it because she had betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't care\Nif I went to the police
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because after canceling my fashion show,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doing so would only damage\Nthe Ashiya Eiko brand name even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:02.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she tried to quit the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to kill her\Nwhile she was still with the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard your father was the\Nfamous detective Mori Kogoro-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't have a change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:46.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:55.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:22:04.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:09.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:16.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:33.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:39.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:49.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:54.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was telling the truth when\NI told you why I wanted you as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted someone with a healthy mind\Nand body such as yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to wear Ashiya Eiko clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Ran-neechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost had your\Nchance to be a model...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come to think of it, where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! I left him there, asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this case\Nhas taken its toll on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's a fan of Ashiya Eiko-san,\Nand he just exposed her crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:23:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he found out I was the one who\Nexposed her crime, he'd murder me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.78,0:24:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.13,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out! You're the ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.36,0:24:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.84,0:24:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Haunted House Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.27,0:24:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.60,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eerie basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.34,0:24:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is a little bit scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.88,0:24:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
